Class NormalDistributedStochasticLotsizingProblem

  • java.lang.Object

    java.io.Serializable

    public class NormalDistributedStochasticLotsizingProblem
extends AbstractStochasticLotSizingProblem
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents a single dynamic stochastic lot sizing problem with normal distributed orders and therefore normal distributed aggregated demand.

    Andi Popp
